    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Feb. 17, 1855</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Your Bible in a<lb/>
                <persName><sic>Bruger's</sic></persName> 12 mo (58x30 cm)<lb/> will make over 1200
                pages<lb/> with the notes. Without the<lb/> notes, perhaps 200 pages
                len<add>?</add>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">As this number of pages would<lb/> be impossible in a 12 mo., I
                do<lb/> not think it worth while to set<lb/> a specimen in
                        <persName><sic>Burger's</sic></persName> a Long<lb/> Primer. You will be
                compelled to use<lb/> a much smaller type.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I return the Bible herewith</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Yours truly,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">Th S MacKellar</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
